  "prompt": "What are the best Indian gaming companies that builds small open world, first-person shooter, 3d games for Ios that you can hire so they can make games for you?",
  "response": "There are several Indian gaming companies that specialize in creating small open-world, first-person shooter, and 3D games for iOS and other platforms. Here are some notable ones you may consider hiring for your game development needs:\n\n1. **Octro**: Known for developing popular mobile games, Octro has experience in various genres, including first-person shooters. Their expertise in mobile game design makes them a solid choice.\n\n2. **Nazara Technologies**: An established player in the Indian gaming market, Nazara has experience in developing diverse game types, including 3D mobile games. They have a solid portfolio and can handle end-to-end development.\n\n3. **Games2win**: This company specializes in mobile games and has a wide array of titles across genres. They may have the expertise you're looking for, particularly for iOS platforms.\n\n4. **Noddle Story**: Focused on creating immersive mobile experiences, Noddle Story has the capability to develop 3D games that might fit your requirements.\n\n5. **Chennai-based Zatun**: Zatun has a longstanding history in game development and has worked on a variety of genres, including 3D and multiplayer games. They have experience with iOS game development.\n\n6. **DreamWalk**: DreamWalk specializes in mobile game development and has experience in building 3D environments. Their portfolio includes various mobile game genres.\n\n7. **Pixel Soar**: This company has a strong focus on mobile game development, including shooter games, and they have experience in creating immersive gaming environments.\n\n8. **Playdemic (now part of Electronic Arts)**: While they are a larger company, they started with a focus on smaller games and could offer services for developing mobile titles.\n\nWhen selecting a game development company, consider reviewing their portfolios, client testimonials, and any previous projects similar to your vision. Additionally, schedule discussions with potential partners to understand their approach and ensure alignment with your project's goals.",
